name: skymeefeeding
0:
”Alexa, start skymee feeder”
”jack feed 1”

skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: skymee feeder
des:
for example, your skymee feeder's name is 'jack', if you want to feeed 1 pack to your pet immediately, say jack feed 1.
or you want to feed 10 packs food to your pet at 21:00, you can say "jack feed 10 at 9 pm".
or you want to play with your pet, you can say "jack shoot" or "jack fire".
or you want to ask your feeder to go forward or go back with 2 steps, you can say "jack go forward for 2" or "jack go back for 2".
or you wan to ask your feeder to turn left or right for 30 degrees, you can say "jack turn 30 to left" or "jack turn 30 to right".
